<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Joel De La O Resume</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .left-panel {
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .profile {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e, #14b8a6);
      color: white;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .profile h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .profile p {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: #0f766e;
    }

    .contact p,
    .skills li,
    .activity li,
    .project li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
    }

    .right-panel .section:first-child {
      border-top: none;
    }

    .main-title {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subhead {
      color: #0f766e;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .muted {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .edu-block,
    .project-block,
    .activity-block {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <aside class="card left-panel">
      <div class="profile">
        <h1>Joel De La O</h1>
        <p>Construction Management Student</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Los Angeles, CA</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 310-350-2951</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> jeffreydelao010@gmail.com</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Microsoft Excel</li>
          <li>Microsoft Word</li>
          <li>Time Management</li>
          <li>Teamwork</li>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Problem Solving</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="card right-panel">
      <div class="section">
        <div class="main-title">Objective</div>
        <p>
          Motivated Construction Management student seeking a construction internship
          to gain hands-on experience, build industry skills, and contribute to
          project success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="edu-block">
          <div class="subhead">California State University, Long Beach</div>
          <p>Bachelor of Science in Construction Management</p>
          <p class="muted">Expected Graduation: 2029</p>
          <p class="muted">GPA: 3.5</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section project">
        <h2>Relevant Project Experience</h2>
        <div class="project-block">
          <div class="subhead">Single-Family Residence Case Study – Westwood, CA</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Analyzed construction planning and development of a residential project.</li>
            <li>Reviewed project scope, scheduling, and cost considerations.</li>
            <li>Collaborated in a team setting to evaluate construction processes.</li>
            <li>Presented findings through organized reports and discussions.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section activity">
        <h2>Activities</h2>
        <div class="activity-block">
          <div class="subhead">Associated General Contractors (AGC)</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Engaged with industry professionals and events.</li>
            <li>Gained exposure to real-world construction practices and networking opportunities.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
